# Arena signup panels · locations & policy

**Primary dev copy:** `~/Desktop/CaribbeanFreedomArena` · preview `npm run dev:arena` → http://localhost:3004

## Boss rule · country live gift ($6 · 3h)

**All country live-gift panels = one-click touch.** No name, email, terms block, or checkbox on the panel.

- Button: `Send Gift · $6.00 · games & talk-show`
- Kicker: per-country viral games · talk-show · funny banter (from `country-live-gift-activity-copy.ts`)
- Legal: link only → `/legal` (“Gift terms · revenue disclosure →”)
- Checkout fallback: `readMemberUsername()` or `Arena Guest` + `guest+{countryId}@caribbeanfreedomarena.app`
- Shared component: `src/components/country-live-gift-checkout-panel.tsx`
  - `variant="intl"` — button row only (International SUITE cards)
  - `variant="gate"` — header + one-click (room overlays)
  - `variant="romantic"` — Colombia pink styling + one-click
- Gate wrapper: `src/components/country-room-live-access-gate.tsx`
- API: `POST /api/payments/country-live-gift/checkout`

