## International SUITE · country panel order

Shared: `international-suite-country-panels.tsx` (used by nav dropdown + full suite scroll)

1. Room cards (built rooms open · Front 12 slots frozen)
2. **Live gift** row · all 12 countries
3. **Dropship** enter + mini products · all 12 countries
4. **East Asia stage** link · Japan + China only

**Pinned at top of country list:** Colombia · UK · Japan · China (`getInternationalSuiteNavCountries()`)

**Built rooms stay open** in International SUITE even when Front 12 sign-in is frozen (`countryHasBuiltSuiteRooms`).

