## When editing live-gift UX

1. Change **one** shared panel (`country-live-gift-checkout-panel.tsx`) — do not reintroduce per-room forms.
2. Update **all** gate mounts if adding a new gated room.
3. Intl card row flows through `international-suite-country-panels.tsx` · all 12 via `getInternationalSuiteNavCountries()`.
4. Terms copy lives in `lib/country-live-gift-checkout.ts` · legal page — not on the one-click panel.
